INSERT INTO `job` VALUES ('10847', 'NJU', '中国光大银行信用卡中心风险管理部招聘-风险政策岗', '发信人: zhou2009 (zhou2009), 信区: JobAndWork<br/>标  题: 中国光大银行信用卡中心风险管理部招聘-风险政策岗<br/>发信站: 南京大学小百合站 (Mon Oct 31 12:43:46 2016)<br/><br/>中国光大银行信用卡中心风险管理部招聘<br/><br/>应聘条件：<br/>1.年龄30岁以下，应届毕业生或有相关工作经验；<br/>2.金融、经济、市场、国际贸易、管理等相关专业；<br/>3.全日制本科及以上学历，应届生要求硕士及以上学历；<br/>4.具备银行对公、零售、信用卡业务风险管理经验的应聘者优先。<br/><br/>岗位描述：风险政策岗<br/><br/>工作内容：<br/>1.负责与分支机构及相关部门沟通、制定、跟踪、优化、培训及解释客户引入、审批及额<br/>度等相关政策和策略；<br/>2.负责对宏观经济形势、同业及行业风险变化趋势的研究，将研究分析结论和对风险趋势<br/>的预判应用于政策制定及完善；<br/>3.负责监控政策的表现情况，在有效控制信用风险的基础上，及时进行风险管理政策的调<br/>整和优化工作；<br/>4.负责与相关项目牵头部门沟通、制定、调整、跟踪和优化项目类客户的引入、审批及授<br/>信政策；<br/>5.根据现有的信用卡政策，对相关项目进行政策审核，提供专业审核意见。<br/><br/>招聘流程：简历投递、笔试、面试和录用等环节。<br/>具体薪资范围在面试通过后由人力部门沟通。<br/><br/>工作地点：北京<br/>邮件标题及简历标题命名：学校+专业+姓名+风险政策岗招聘<br/>有意者请将您的简历发送至mayuchen@cebbank.com<br/><br/><br/>--<br/>[1;35m※ 来源:．南京大学小百合站 http://bbs.nju.edu.cn [FROM: 172.28.147.70][m<br/>[m[1;37m※ yika1985 于 Oct 31 20:43:47 2016 转贴�[FROM: yika.nju.edu.cn][m<br/>', '2016-10-31 20:43:00', 'FULL', '0');
INSERT INTO `job` VALUES ('10848', 'NJU', '2017苏州超锐微电子招聘模拟IC设计、嵌入式软件、数', '发信人: xstkl ([color=gold]【古韵泰州】国物院[/color]), 信区: JobAndWork<br/>标  题: 2017苏州超锐微电子招聘模拟IC设计、嵌入式软件、数�发信站: 南京大学小百合站 (Mon Oct 31 13:53:24 2016)<br/><br/><br/>2017苏州超锐微电子有限公司校园招聘开始啦！<br/>一、宣讲会时间地点：<br/>宣讲会时间：11月05日14:00-17:30；<br/>宣讲会地点：东南大学四牌楼校区-礼东202；<br/>二、公司简介：<br/>苏州超锐微电子有限公司是苏州地区一家重量级Fabless集成电路设计企业，坐落于苏州国<br/>家高新开发区苏州创业园内，拥有1000平方米的综合办公场所。公司一直秉承“超越梦想<br/>，锐意进取”的经营理念，致力于中高端消费类电子芯片的自主研发专注于中高端芯片设<br/>计和销售，产品方向包括：计算机周边接口控制器芯片、无线WiFi和有线网络控制器芯片<br/>、MEMS 传感器芯片。公司超过90%的芯片产品填补国内技术空白，产品领域具有一流的行<br/>业影响力。公司属于“国家集成电路设计企业”、“江苏省软件企业”、“江苏省高新技<br/>术企业”，“江苏省博士后创新实践基地”、“苏州市集成电路工程技术研究中心”、“<br/>苏州市企业技术中心”。<br/>公司研发团队汇聚了优秀IC设计人才，其中博士3人，硕士14人，国家万人计划1人，科技<br/>部科技创新创业人才1人，江苏省“333”工程人才1人，姑苏重点产业紧缺人才1人，苏州<br/>市创新创业领军人才1人，苏州高新区高层次紧缺人才2人，其余人员均毕业于南京大学、<br/>西安交通大学、浙江大学、东南大学、苏州大学等国内知名院校。<br/>公司一直坚持自主创新，已申请了60多项发明专利，其中12项获得授权，获得国家计算机<br/>软件著作权21项、集成电路布图设计权15项、江苏省认定的高新技术产品15项、江苏省认<br/>定的软件产品5项、商标权2项，积累了50余项完全自主知识产权的IP技术。公司于2009年<br/>获得江苏省专利奖，于2008年、2011年、2012年分别获得苏州市科学技术进步二等奖，于<br/>2013年、2015年分别获苏州市科学技术进步奖二等奖。<br/>公司集成电路产品，累计销售3000多万颗芯片，60％实现进口替代，创造销售收入6000多<br/>万元，毛利3000多万元，且每年以1.5倍的速度快速稳步增长，其中40％出口到香港和日韩<br/>市场，客户群业已覆盖联想、长城电脑、京华数码、爱国者、力特、矽霸、腾达、清华同<br/>方、富士康、九洲电器等系统大厂。<br/>公司倡导人性化的管理，并为员工提供具有竞争力的薪酬待遇和良好的发展平台。我们期<br/>待着各位青年才俊的加盟，与公司一起发现自我、实现自我、超越自我，共创属于我们美<br/>好的未来！<br/><br/>公司地址：苏州新区竹园路209号苏州创业园3号楼1201室<br/>公司网站：www.supereal.com.cn<br/><br/>三、岗位需求<br/>1、模拟IC设计工程师（5人）<br/>职位描述：<br/>模拟电路模块建模、设计、仿真和验证。<br/>任职要求：<br/>1、硕士，电子、通信及相关专业；<br/>2、熟悉Verilog-AMS语言或Matlab建模；<br/>3、熟练掌握模拟电路原理，相关EDA工具和流程；<br/>4、良好的团队合作精神和沟通能力；<br/><br/>2、嵌入式软件工程师（5人）<br/>职位描述：<br/>基于ARM或者DSP的嵌入式系统软件开发。<br/>任职要求：<br/>1、本科及以上，电子、通信、计算机及相关专业；<br/>2、熟练掌握C语言；<br/>3、熟悉单片机或者ARM编程；<br/>4、具有良好的团队精神和沟通能力。<br/><br/>3、数字IC设计工程师（5人）<br/>职位描述：<br/>数字电路模块算法、编码、仿真和验证。<br/>任职要求：<br/>1、本科及以上，电子、通信及相关专业；<br/>2、熟悉C和Verilog语言；<br/>3、熟练掌握数字电路原理和数字信号处理；<br/>4、良好的团队合作精神和沟通能力。<br/><br/>4、系统开发工程师（5人）<br/>职位描述：<br/>电路测试调试、单片机开发、功能验证、PCB和应用方案开发。<br/>任职要求：<br/>1、本科及以上，电子、通信、计算机及相关专业；<br/>2、掌握电子电路原理和C语言；<br/>3、熟悉PCB绘制；<br/>4、良好的动手能力、团队合作精神和沟通能力。<br/><br/>5、IC后端设计工程师（2人）<br/>职位描述：<br/>芯片的后端设计、验证、Tapeout<br/>任职要求：<br/>1、本科及以上，电子及相关专业；<br/>2、掌握电子电路原理；<br/>3、有后端设计或电路版图设计经验为佳；<br/>4、良好的团队合作精神和沟通能力。<br/>四、简历投递<br/>1、招聘邮箱：hr@supereal.com.cn（注：应聘邮件请按固定主题格式“学校名称+应聘岗<br/>位+姓名”，应聘简历请以附件形式发送，方便下载和筛选，谢谢配合。）<br/>2、联系方式：张小姐0512-68416872   18862347861<br/>3、收到简历后，我们会尽快联系您的！期待您的加入。<br/><br/>--<br/>[1;36m※ 来源:．南京大学小百合站 http://bbs.nju.edu.cn [FROM: 121.227.185.145][m<br/>[m[1;37m※ yika1985 于 Oct 31 20:43:51 2016 转贴�[FROM: yika.nju.edu.cn][m<br/>', '2016-10-31 20:43:00', 'FULL', '0');
INSERT INTO `job` VALUES ('10849', 'NJU', '招聘: 美国顶尖交易公司：Junior C++ Developer-高', '发信人: hughsheep (hughsheep), 信区: JobAndWork<br/>标  题:  招聘: 美国顶尖交易公司：Junior C++ Developer-高�发信站: 南京大学小百合站 (Mon Oct 31 13:59:39 2016)<br/><br/><br/>招聘: 美国顶尖交易公司：Junior C++ Developer-高性能交易系统-上海<br/>• Cutting-edge technologies<br/>• Talented and strong co-workers<br/>• Website: www.akunacapital.com<br/><br/>Who We Are<br/>Akuna Capital is a derivatives trading firm headquartered in downtown Chicago<br/>that specializes in market making and arbitrage.  Akuna started with five<br/>employees in 2011 and we now have over 140. In 2014 we grew by 84%, opening<br/>our first international office in Shanghai. Our founders remain a strong part<br/>of the company and work alongside junior members, building Akuna together. We<br/>compete directly with the largest market making and arbitrage firms in the<br/>world. We develop our own software strategies, algorithms, and models. We also<br/>have floor traders so we are not entirely an electronic firm. We have no<br/>clients and trade only using the firm’s own money from its partners. We use<br/>cutting-edge technology to build our low latency platform. Unlike other firms,<br/>we do not have legacy code and are therefore able to implement new strategies<br/>to be more agile in the creation of our trading systems. Other trading firms<br/>keep their quant, development, and trading teams very separate. At Akuna, we<br/>are a very collaborative team and believe that this type of integration is<br/>vital for success in this industry.<br/>公司总部位于美国芝加哥，在上海，波士顿设有分部，我们是美国最大的期权产品做市商<br/>之一。交易主要集中在芝加哥商品交易所，芝加哥期权交易所，ISE, 纽约证券交易所，和<br/>纳斯达克市场, 涉及的产品包含股票指数期权，利率期权及期货 (国债) ，外汇期权以及<br/>商品(谷物，牲畜，石油，和黄金)期货期权。我们有经验丰富的优秀交易员和创新开拓的<br/>IT精英。Akuna上海目前正在组建团队，打造最前沿的期权期货交易系统。在这里，你可以<br/>更加接近市场，建立自动化的交易系统。这里是技术和市场结合最前沿的地方。（我们是<br/>属于做市商，主要做期权产品，期货）<br/>We are seeking Junior C++ Developers to join our innovative and growing<br/>technology team at Akuna. You will work alongside our trading and software<br/>team to design and implement elegant solutions to complex and interesting<br/>problems.<br/>What you’ll do as a Junior Developer at Akuna:<br/>• Junior Developers at Akuna have the opportunity to use cutting-edge<br/>technology while working on high performance/low latency systems.<br/>• We offer a team-based approach to trading and software engineering,<br/>believing that productive integration of the two groups is vital for success<br/>in this industry.<br/>• Akuna loves Junior Developers who are self-starters and have the ability to<br/>work without a constant need for guidance. We value innovation and hard work,<br/>and want you to make an impact in the firm, even as a junior member.<br/>• Whether you are interested in trading infrastructure, algorithms, models,<br/>exchange gateways, performance engineering, hardware, data capture and<br/>analysis, there’s work to be done.<br/><br/>What would make you a top-notch candidate?<br/>• Pursuing a BS/MS/ PhD in Computer Science, Engineering, Math, Physics or<br/>related field<br/>• 0-2 years’ experience in C++<br/>• Demonstrated experience with distributed systems will be a big plus Strong<br/>analytic and problem-solving skills<br/>• Good English communication skill Create an easily understood and testable<br/>codebase that can change as quickly as market conditions require<br/>• Passion for innovation and building systems from the ground up<br/>• Ability to adapt to an ever-changing environment Self-starter attitude with<br/>the ability to work independently<br/>Email your resume to lucy.luo@akunacapital.com<br/><br/><br/>--<br/>[1;34m※ 来源:．南京大学小百合站 http://bbs.nju.edu.cn [FROM: 66.151.26.243][m<br/>[m[1;37m※ yika1985 于 Oct 31 20:43:55 2016 转贴�[FROM: yika.nju.edu.cn][m<br/>', '2016-10-31 20:43:00', 'FULL', '0');
INSERT INTO `job` VALUES ('10850', 'NJU', '[金融]：Python Web Developer�交易系统开发- 上海', '发信人: hughsheep (hughsheep), 信区: JobAndWork<br/>标  题:  [金融]：Python Web Developer�交易系统开发- 上海<br/>发信站: 南京大学小百合站 (Mon Oct 31 13:59:56 2016)<br/><br/><br/>[金融]：Python Web Developer�交易系统开发- 上海<br/>• Key skill: Python, JavaScript, English communication<br/>• Training in Chicago<br/>• Work closely with Quant and trading team<br/>• Learn and use Options and futures knowledge<br/>• Website: www.akunacapital.com<br/>Send CV to Shanghaicareers@akunacapital.com<br/><br/>Akuna Capital is a derivative trading firm headquartered in downtown Chicago<br/>that specializes in market making and arbitrage.  Akuna started with five<br/>employees in 2011 and we now have over 150. In 2014 we grew by 84%, opening<br/>our first international office in Shanghai. Our founders remain a strong part<br/>of the company and work alongside junior members, building Akuna together. We<br/>compete directly with the largest market making and arbitrage firms in the<br/>world. We develop our own software strategies, algorithms, and models. We also<br/>have floor traders so we are not entirely an electronic firm. We have no<br/>clients and trade only using the firm’s own money from its partners. We use<br/>cutting-edge technology to build our low latency platform. Unlike other firms,<br/>we do not have legacy code and are therefore able to implement new strategies<br/>to be more agile in the creation of our trading systems. Other trading firms<br/>keep their quant, development, and trading teams very separate. At Akuna, we<br/>are a very collaborative team and believe that this type of integration is<br/>vital for success in this industry.<br/>公司总部位于美国芝加哥，在上海，波士顿设有分部，我们是美国最大的期权产品做市商<br/>之一。交易主要集中在芝加哥商品交易所，芝加哥期权交易所，ISE, 纽约证券交易所，和<br/>纳斯达克市场, 涉及的产品包含股票指数期权，利率期权及期货 (国债) ，外汇期权以及<br/>商品(谷物，牲畜，石油，和黄金)期货期权。我们有经验丰富的优秀交易员和创新开拓的<br/>IT精英。Akuna上海目前正在组建团队，打造最前沿的期权期货交易系统。在这里，你可以<br/>更加接近市场，建立自动化的交易系统。这里是技术和市场结合最前沿的地方。（我们是<br/>属于做市商，主要做期权产品，期货）<br/>We are looking for a Full Stack Web Developer who has strong web and<br/>application design skills to help our existing web development team bring our<br/>applications to the next level.  You will build real-time data visualization<br/>and parameter configuration tools to directly aid traders in assessing risk<br/>and strategy. At Akuna Capital, your participation means creating the tools<br/>which developers, traders and support personnel will be using every day to<br/>compete on the market.<br/>Our web application backbends are based on Tornado, the asynchronous web<br/>framework for Python. We take full advantage of Tornado\'s coroutine feature to<br/>create elegant asynchronous servers that scale efficiently. We utilize<br/>websockets to create live-updating displays to ensure traders have access to<br/>the most up-to-date information as quickly as possible. We power our front-<br/>ends with React to focus our development on making the best possible<br/>representations of our data. In addition to supporting traders, we also create<br/>monitoring applications for server support and development teams to help them<br/>better understand current resource utilization and notify them when services<br/>need attention.<br/><br/>The ideal candidate is very comfortable with Python and JavaScript, loves the<br/>web, keeps up-to-date with new technology and is excited at the prospect of<br/>working with our team to take our web applications to the next level. You will<br/>be the first Web Developer in Shanghai office, will work closely with Quant<br/>team, learn and use quant knowledge with web development.<br/>Key Skills:<br/>• 3+ years of professional Python experience<br/>• 3+ years of professional Front-end JavaScript Experience (with HTML/CSS3)<br/>• Designing &amp; writing REST or server push APIs<br/>• Experience with front-end User Experience (UX) and Design<br/>• Comfortable with Linux and source control (git)<br/>• Strong communication skills and works well in teams<br/>• Provide support during releases and production incidents<br/>• Good English communication skill<br/>Qualities that Make Great Candidates:<br/>• Experience with React JS<br/>• Previous experience with asynchronous frameworks (especially coroutines)<br/>• Bachelor\'s, Master\'s or Ph.D. in Computer Science, Engineering or<br/>equivalent<br/>• Familiar with Agile methodologies<br/><br/>--<br/>[1;36m※ 来源:．南京大学小百合站 http://bbs.nju.edu.cn [FROM: 66.151.26.243][m<br/>[m[1;37m※ yika1985 于 Oct 31 20:43:58 2016 转贴�[FROM: yika.nju.edu.cn][m<br/>', '2016-10-31 20:43:00', 'FULL', '0');
